### Intelligent Customer Support API — sample requests
### Use with the VS Code "REST Client" extension, or translate to curl.
@base = http://localhost:3000

### Health
GET {{base}}/health

### Create a ticket
# @name create
POST {{base}}/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": "CUST-1",
  "customer_email": "jane@example.com",
  "customer_name": "Jane Doe",
  "subject": "Cannot log in",
  "description": "I cannot access my account after the latest update. This is critical.",
  "metadata": { "source": "web_form", "browser": "Chrome", "device_type": "desktop" }
}

### Create with auto-classification
POST {{base}}/tickets?auto_classify=true
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer_id": "CUST-2",
  "customer_email": "bob@example.com",
  "customer_name": "Bob Jones",
  "subject": "App crashes on upload",
  "description": "The app crashes with an error every time I upload a file. Production down.",
  "metadata": { "source": "chat", "device_type": "mobile" }
}

### Validation error (missing email, short description)
POST {{base}}/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{ "customer_id": "CUST-3", "customer_name": "X", "subject": "Hi", "description": "short",
  "metadata": { "source": "web_form", "device_type": "desktop" } }

### Bulk import (CSV) with auto-classify
POST {{base}}/tickets/import?format=csv&auto_classify=true
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----b

------b
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample_tickets.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

< ../samples/sample_tickets.csv
------b--

### List all
GET {{base}}/tickets

### Combined filter
GET {{base}}/tickets?category=billing_question&priority=high

### Get one  (paste an id from the create response)
GET {{base}}/tickets/{{create.response.body.id}}

### Update (partial) -> resolve
PUT {{base}}/tickets/{{create.response.body.id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "status": "resolved", "assigned_to": "agent-7" }

### Auto-classify an existing ticket
POST {{base}}/tickets/{{create.response.body.id}}/auto-classify

### Delete
DELETE {{base}}/tickets/{{create.response.body.id}}
